---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — SFCE Learning"
  description="Privacy policy for SFCE Learning. We do not collect personal data, use cookies, or track users."
  canonicalPath="/privacy/"
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 sm:py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-text-primary dark:text-dark-text-primary mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <div class="space-y-8 text-text-secondary dark:text-dark-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        <strong class="text-text-primary dark:text-dark-text-primary">Last updated:</strong> April 15, 2026
      </p>

      <p>
        SFCE Learning (<a href="https://sfcelearning.com" class="text-accent dark:text-dark-accent hover:underline">sfcelearning.com</a>)
        is a free, open-source study guide for the Symfony Framework Certification Exam. Your privacy matters to us,
        and we have designed this application to operate without collecting any personal information.
      </p>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-primary dark:text-dark-text-primary mb-3">No Personal Data Collection</h2>
        <p>
          We do not collect, store, process, or transmit any personal data. There are no user accounts,
          no registration forms, no email collection, and no contact forms on this website. No information
          about you is ever sent to our servers or any third-party service.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-primary dark:text-dark-text-primary mb-3">No Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          This website does not use cookies of any kind — no session cookies, no tracking cookies,
          no analytics cookies, and no third-party cookies. As such, no cookie consent banner is required.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-primary dark:text-dark-text-primary mb-3">Local Storage</h2>
        <p>
          This application uses your browser's <strong class="text-text-primary dark:text-dark-text-primary">localStorage</strong> API
          to save two types of preferences directly on your device:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-3 space-y-1">
          <li><strong class="text-text-primary dark:text-dark-text-primary">Study progress</strong> — which references you have marked as completed</li>
          <li><strong class="text-text-primary dark:text-dark-text-primary">Theme preference</strong> — your chosen color scheme (light, dark, or system)</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3">
          This data is stored exclusively in your browser and is never transmitted to any server.
          You can clear it at any time through your browser settings. Unlike cookies, localStorage data
          is not sent with HTTP requests and cannot be used for cross-site tracking.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-primary dark:text-dark-text-primary mb-3">No Analytics or Tracking</h2>
        <p>
          We do not use any analytics services (such as Google Analytics), tracking pixels, fingerprinting,
          or any other mechanism to monitor your behavior on this website. We have no interest in tracking
          how you use this application.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-primary dark:text-dark-text-primary mb-3">No Third-Party Data Sharing</h2>
        <p>
          Since we do not collect any data, there is nothing to share with third parties. This website
          does not integrate with any advertising networks, social media platforms, or data brokers.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-primary dark:text-dark-text-primary mb-3">External Links</h2>
        <p>
          This application contains links to external websites, primarily the official Symfony documentation
          and PHP documentation. These external sites have their own privacy policies, and we are not
          responsible for their content or data practices.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-primary dark:text-dark-text-primary mb-3">Hosting</h2>
        <p>
          This website is hosted on <strong class="text-text-primary dark:text-dark-text-primary">GitHub Pages</strong>.
          GitHub may collect basic server logs (such as IP addresses) as part of their infrastructure.
          For details, please refer to
          <a href="https://docs.github.com/en/site-policy/privacy-policies/github-general-privacy-statement" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent dark:text-dark-accent hover:underline">GitHub's Privacy Statement</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-primary dark:text-dark-text-primary mb-3">Open Source</h2>
        <p>
          This application is open source. You can review the entire source code to verify these privacy
          claims at our
          <a href="https://github.com/kardasz/sfce" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent dark:text-dark-accent hover:underline">GitHub repository</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-text-primary dark:text-dark-text-primary mb-3">Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          If we make any changes to this privacy policy, we will update the "Last updated" date at the top
          of this page. Given the nature of this application, significant changes are unlikely.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
